text: Stephen P. Synnott is an American astronomer.IAU retrieved 29th August 2010 He is also a scientist for the Voyager program.daviddarling.info retrieved 29th August 2010 He discovered several moons of Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, and Neptune. He discovered Metis, Puck, Larissa, Proteus, and Thebe. The minor planet 6154 Stevesynnott was named after him.Dictionary of minor planet names Lutz D.
